{"tid":1280350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰後工作】琴日兩單大型抄車事件反映出我地好多野要做","createTime":"2019-07-03T02:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T07:52:28.000Z","uid":15276,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cd861c5a67beb332c950116e17c21c2ca3153c","tid":1280350,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:57:00.000Z","msg":"抗爭後真係會忙過抗爭十萬倍，隨便list一list都好多樣野要同時做：<br />\n<br />\n1. 保障自身安全，不要被捕！<br />\n2. 喺懸崖邊拯救失意嘅隊友<br />\n3. 真假訊息滿天飛，Fact Check所有消息<br />\n4. 對抗對方強勢打壓手段、抽後算帳、白色恐怖<br />\n5. 繼續調查政府同黑警過往嘅罪行<br />\n6. 說服「民意」，文宣組努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7. 準備選舉事宜、搵人出選、說服身邊嘅人唔好投非民主派<br />\n8. 尋求國外支援<br />\n9. 思考下一次行動、準備物資<br />\n10. 因大部分監管渠道已失效，聯同記者、議員、市民合力監察公權和警察行動<br />\n11. 調理好個人身心，休息!!<br />\n<br />\n應該仲有好多野要做未數得晒，所以話香港人真係好攰，我地真係丁點分裂嘅本錢都無，對方係出絕力打壓緊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外琴日兩單大型炒車事件Fact Check：<br />\n<br />\n-中國ddos事件：今次未必關中國事、唔係因為ddos導致CloudFlare死機、平時中美一直有互相ddos攻擊對方。<br />\n<br />\n-興民邨搜捕事件：已證實係非法禁錮案件，唔關乎任何示威者事。<br />\n<br />\n明白而家每個人都會神經緊張，消息亂飛，炒車都在所難免，不過令大家提高警覺都係一件好事，一齊注意有無濫捕情況同埋網絡安全！"},{"pid":"b70dec01f130375dce0d01f11f55a2a4e73e9c12","tid":1280350,"uid":15276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d126717f41e7d3feec6a2741a35f8445f57a19","tid":1280350,"uid":258302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29e12f345729935038c5528ac7f24cf0af9fb8b3","tid":1280350,"uid":253127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47cb7f25a297d49a6a0df87faa98953fa3e7d946","tid":1280350,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97e8862b585dee881823821b54bc3b6c7cc02cf","tid":1280350,"uid":253127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:08:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fa66c1859d8ffc0775694d321bdc2d39d905492","tid":1280350,"uid":33939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"擒日講咗，但一柒咗嘅嘢就冇人理，一係就唔肯面對真相，話cloudflare係講大話，完全唔會反思。所以中伏，俾人煸動真係好容易。"},{"pid":"258a27f31f66b6157464b20eb02ad25b3c09e281","tid":1280350,"uid":258115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d19e1a9f0da622c1af229801252b48eaf5a3207","tid":1280350,"uid":145520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"係, 唔理又唔得, 只能講提高警覺同冷靜分析..."},{"pid":"f7b4285e40e99e5a53eff04fca49e0330561dff6","tid":1280350,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d19e1a9f0da622c1af229801252b48eaf5a3207","tid":1280350,"uid":145520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"係, 唔理又唔得, 只能講提高警覺同冷靜分析..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"你叫人fact check，就會俾人派膠，俾人屌"},{"pid":"7dade714cf91e59e05d9b6d0db155197482b18f1","tid":1280350,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62bedb04c50ef62815443fa7266cc66d8d4bb56","tid":1280350,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:40:47.000Z","msg":"好攰 但係要加油"},{"pid":"e1c877ca5540c88e32d3a1ca2a3c18502febcb40","tid":1280350,"uid":15